OL,3,CIs Europe too hot for school holidays?
OL,4,CChoosing a destination by its weather
OL,6,FMillions of British families head to
OL,7,Fsouthern Europe during the school
OL,8,Fholidays every July and August.
OL,10,FBut with temperatures regularly
OL,11,Fclimbing well above 40C in parts of
OL,12,FSpain, Italy and Greece, many are
OL,13,Fasking whether the traditional
OL,14,FMediterranean summer holiday is
OL,15,Fbecoming too hot.
OL,17,FSo should we change where we go during
OL,18,Fthe school summer holidays?
OL,20,FIt comes down to heat tolerance.
OL,26,@sD@WOX
