OL,3,CIs Europe too hot for school holidays?
OL,4,CChoosing a destination by its weather
OL,6,FA beach resort with shade, sea access
OL,7,Fand air conditioning is very different
OL,8,Ffrom exploring historic cities,
OL,9,Fhiking, or visiting theme parks during
OL,10,Fa heatwave.
OL,12,FLess southern-based and more Atlantic-
OL,13,Finfluenced locations - such as parts
OL,14,Fof northern Spain, western France,
OL,15,FIreland, the UK, Scandinavia or the
OL,16,FBaltic - may offer a more comfortable
OL,17,Fbalance of sunshine and heat for some
OL,18,Ftravellers.
