OL,3,CIs Europe too hot for school holidays?
OL,4,CChoosing a destination by its weather
OL,6,FThe Alps are stunning in the summer,
OL,7,Foffering a combination of elevation
OL,8,Fmaking for less intense heat and
OL,9,Fbeautiful lakes providing calmer
OL,10,Fwaters - which appeals more to some
OL,11,Ffamilies.
OL,13,FClimate change is shifting the comfort
OL,14,Fzone. As average temperatures rise,
OL,15,Fthe number of days when some southern
OL,16,FEuropean destinations experience
OL,17,Fextreme heat is increasing.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
