OL,3,CIs Europe too hot for school holidays?
OL,4,CChoosing a destination by its weather
OL,6,FThat does not mean they become
OL,7,Funsuitable, but travellers may
OL,8,Fincreasingly factor heat risk into
OL,9,Ftheir choice in the same way they
OL,10,Fconsider rainfall or flight time or
OL,11,Ftime zone.
OL,13,FWhy are European summers becoming
OL,14,Fhotter?
OL,16,FThere are several reasons why
OL,17,Ftemperatures are much higher than they
OL,18,Fused to be through the summer months.
OL,20,FDoes being on the coast make the heat
OL,21,Fmore manageable?
