OL,3,CIs Europe too hot for school holidays?
OL,4,CChoosing a destination by its weather
OL,6,FIf winds are blowing from the south or
OL,7,Fsoutheast, they can bring very hot air
OL,8,Ffrom Iberia, North Africa or
OL,9,Fcontinental Europe over coastal areas
OL,10,Fand islands.
OL,12,FA sea breeze cannot always overcome a
OL,13,Flarge-scale 'heat dome'.
OL,15,FThe Atlantic coast is different from
OL,16,Fthe Mediterranean.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
