OL,3,CIs Europe too hot for school holidays?
OL,4,CChoosing a destination by its weather
OL,6,FThese warmer waters prevent the usual
OL,7,Fcool sea breezes developing, and stop
OL,8,Ftemperatures from falling overnight.
OL,10,FAdded to this, the extra moisture
OL,11,Fseeps into the atmosphere increasing
OL,12,Fthe humidity and uncomfortable feel.
