PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1784357294
OL,3,CIs Europe too hot for school holidays?
OL,4,CChoosing a destination by its weather
OL,6,FThe future of the European summer
OL,7,Fholiday may not be about abandoning
OL,8,Fthe Mediterranean but about becoming
OL,9,Fmore selective.
OL,11,FAs summers heat up, the best
OL,12,Fdestination may be the one that offers
OL,13,Fconsistent manageable weather which
OL,14,Fcan be enjoyed, rather than the
OL,15,Fendurance of some very relentless high
OL,16,Ftemperatures.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/10
